summary:
A highly intuitive and empathetic person, responsible and mature. I am self-motivated and passionate about helping people.
Experienced Massage Therapist with a demonstrated history of working in the health and wellness industry. Skilled in Medical Massage, Pregnancy Massage, Trigger Point Therapy, Deep Tissue Massage, and Sports Massage. Strong healthcare services professional with a Bachelor's degree in Physiotherapy from the Medical University of Pleven in Bulgaria. 
I possess strong interpersonal skills and effective team-working acquired from participating in two Work&Travel programs in The USA and two Erasmus+ traineeships in Poland and the Netherlands.  These opportunities opened my mind to new ideas, cultures and information.
Currently, I am a self-employed massage therapist at my own practice in Amsterdam - Transcendence Massage by Viktoria.
